<li><a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/webworkify">webworkify</a> - composable web workers for browserify</li>
<h2>files</h2>
<li><a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/fuse4js">fuse4js</a> - write filesystem driver in js</li>
