<li><a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/box-intersect">box-intersect</a> - fast any dimensional box intersection detection</li>
<li><a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/surface-nets">surface-nets</a> - extracts level sets in any dimension</li>
<li><a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/voxelize">voxelize</a> - voxelize a mesh</li>
<h2>images</h2>
<li><a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/indico.io">indico.io</a> - facial emotion recognition and facial feature extraction</li>
<h2>text</h2>
